>\n<br />\n<br />\n錯在唔係真心鐘意個女仔又要同個女仔一齊囉，<br />\n你條撚樣問得呢句都知你無真正愛過一個人<br />\n<br />\n同你講多都嘥氣"},{"pid":"f3c6b93f1f03e1bc1bd4fe61773a036937a23292","tid":500860,"uid":7491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"170/83 大肥鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b965f9307b8bc16cc5feecfff4bc360343dde1cb","tid":500860,"uid":14055,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔介意，仲會更加愛錫佢，俾多d 安全感佢<br />\n個男既因爲咁樣而飛左佢 ，叫佢仆街死啦，呃蝦條去5p 啦，大把雞你叫<br />\n滿意未？</blockquote><br />\n個男仔錯響邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錯在唔係真心鐘意個女仔又要同個女仔一齊囉，<br />\n你條撚樣問得呢句都知你無真正愛過一個人<br />\n<br />\n同你講多都嘥氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又未結婚，覺得唔啱自己做唔到夫妻，分手再搵過個有咩問題，其他人分手嘅原因都係嫌對方某啲缺點啫，唔通佢地講句「因了解而分開」就特別高尚？"},{"pid":"d58dffea7dd57b7c0242aca4b1110432516db6c5","tid":500860,"uid":43875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"負皮 上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da15fdf069ac0c5949e0c239de297dcb0ddf9de","tid":500860,"uid":84367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b7aabcba9045707dac1da269ff0093c11f099ce0","tid":500860,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8660a08354fd81cf4a57a36af198a2bb9fb50e4b","tid":500860,"uid":63509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T18:27:13.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n抄人又唔撚認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5333c6e4e1ebcd7cbc1b9c00d11aac630eb4b2ed","tid":500860,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T20:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持絲打，結左婚先好比人屌！ 拍下散拖就要屌埋閪，條仆街仔味好著數？ 記住，你兩塊閪皮好撚值錢嫁！ 如果你想破處，不如拎去eBay 拍賣啦！ 最少都值幾萬， 你比mk仔屌完，一都拎唔返啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"